{"tid":1165334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"雙魚座嘅你 入下黎圍爐取暖","createTime":"2019-05-21T17:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T10:29:08.000Z","uid":240363,"like":30,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"0b13e3dfc4c99d8da93db6898d92b07f83ed8865","tid":1165334,"uid":240363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:18:37.000Z","msg":"作為一個正宗嘅雙魚<br />\n其實我覺得真係好煩，成日都好多疑多愁善感<br />\n覺得全世界啲人都唔鍾意自己，人哋尻up一句<br />\n就會覺得。啊！佢唔鍾意我點算好？<br />\n大圈子入面，見到啲朋友眼神一變，就覺得佢哋私底下一定有講過我。<br />\n或者就係因為咁樣，我真係唔識點同朋友相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小劇場太多啦</span><br />\n男朋友嘅行為舉止一有少少奇怪，就會又冧得好多，好多時都會冧，我係米癲左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係因為諗得太多，我會成日都好唔舒服<br />\n焦慮到要食藥先瞓得着<br />\n唉，純粹發洩下！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我真係唔想成為一隻多疑嘅咸魚！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有冇啲雙魚座嘅朋友？<br />\n想知道，世界上我吾係孤單多疑嘅魚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85dff2c58b22a40e1324ef8642bafe440ce3750","tid":1165334,"uid":16775,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:20:44.000Z","msg":"無自信到仆街<br />\n佢唔覆我一陣就會諗我係咪講錯野做錯野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0cca2a22fd0b891903e437b9d035f7cf2bb3bf","tid":1165334,"uid":209692,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:20:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6857c6d98a1d1796ea10995298cd9935dd1994d2","tid":1165334,"uid":42796,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:23:14.000Z","msg":"唔好因為自己雙魚座比理由自己成日FF<br />\n<br />\n利申：雙魚座"},{"pid":"a19233337de8ea75979b9827d07dce39e2c8ee32","tid":1165334,"uid":240363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d0cca2a22fd0b891903e437b9d035f7cf2bb3bf","tid":1165334,"uid":209692,"like":5,"dislike":1,"sco